title: Kuki
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Ovo, Chinese, Japanese, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Carry-out Japanese and Chinese restaurant located in the same shopping center as Santoni's. Offers a separate menu of vegetarian/vegan dishes called healthy choice. Has kung pao tofu, vegi-sesame beef, a few vegan sushi options, brown rice or white rice, and for the combination lunch boxes you can replace meat with tofu or imitation meat.
